Travel Agent should able to plan, research and book the trip for you.

So this 3 are the main areas a travel agent should remember.
But there are alot of things should be kept in mind before doing all this things

1. The travel should be according to the hobbies and things the person wants to do (Personalized Travel)
2. Be a guide to the how to explore the destination
3. know the timing and weather of the place to travel
4. Budget friendly
5. documentation and safety the things
6. Troubleshoot all the things

So creating an AI agent to do this all things.

First I will start with the sub-agent that will create a persons data so that it will have personized touch in planning

Agent will ask some questions that will be saved in vectorstore as characterstic of the person and then this characterstics will be used as base point to the travel points.

